check first letter of the string 
	if it not a seperat 
		{ we enter a word  count +1 if in_word = 0 and then in_word = 1 ,
		 put that letter in array[i]}, move to next letter }
check the next letter
	if it is a seperater
		{ we get out of a word ( in_word =0), and the i ++, move to next index for array}
	else 
		{ put that in array[i]}
	move to next
until the string reach '\0'
add 0 on the the string last index;
